formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1. Estimated amount under column 'Payment of Taxes, cess, fees, charges, premiums, interest etc. to any Statutory Authority' is not showing the amount as certified at the time of application. At the time of issuing certificate for registration dated 05/11/2018 the amount was mentioned at Rs. 3,19,20,000 .
2.Because of technical limitation, Amount of estimated Payment of Taxes, cess, fees, charges, premiums, interest etc. to any Statutory Authority under sr. no. 1. b. cannot be changed and hence is without taking into consideration the GST liability pursuant to change in taxability with effect from 1 April 2019.
3. Agreement to sale entered into are subject to verification of registration with appropriate authority, if any.
4.Unit price in case of sold units also includes total consideration received or receivable for the unit which includes amount mentionedin sale deed or agreement to sale and any other amount directly or indirectly received from allotee for the purchase of the property such as Construction agreement, if any.
